Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,excelsis Deo. All glory be to thee, O Lord. All glory be to thee. The problem with the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,world is it says, all glory be to me. Thee, not me. That is the difference between enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and hell. A little technicality there. All right, so thank you. The lecture today is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,about something or other. Let's see what the hell it says here. Oh, what does it say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:02:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,here? Oh, what does it say the lecture is about today? Spiritual practice in everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,life. Okay. That ought to be interesting. We'll see what comes up. How many are new
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,today? Oh, so we always have a sprinkling of new. Okay. Well, we have the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,subject for today is going to take up most of the time, so we won't do as much a review
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,as we have usually done in the past. We'll just put up slide one for sake of familiarity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and re-explain it, because we're going to spend more time on spiritual practice in everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,life, because that's what it's all about. Now, the map of consciousness is an exponential
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,logarithmic, I don't know, logarithmic. It goes from one to one. It goes from one to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:03:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,a thousand. It goes from one to a thousand. The numbers are to the base 10. So, 150 means
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,10 times 10 times 10, 150 times. 400 means 10 times 10 times 10, 400 times to the exponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,400. Therefore, an increase in a level of consciousness is very, very significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a few points makes a tremendous difference. We noticed that in, we're going to be doing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a lecture in medicine, and academic medicine calibrates at 440. Holistic medicine, the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,kind I always practice, calibrates at about 445. And it's not just academic, it's experiential.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:04:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the extra five points doesn't sound like much, but when you're, you know, you're
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,talking 455 times that many number, you can see it's quite a bit of difference. And the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,clinical response is quite a bit different between academic medicine and clinical medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And my ear's falling off again, right? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the other thing we want to clarify is that the kinesiologic response is, kinesiologic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,response is, is, is, is, is, is, is, is, is, is, is, is, is, is, is, is, is, is, is, is, is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is, is, extremely useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not a personal response. A lot of people will write me and they'll say, how come you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated something at so-and-so? You know, like I have a personal stake in it. I couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,care less. It's just a number. It's just a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The number is independent of opinion. The number indicates essence. The difficulty with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the human life is the differentiation between perception and essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ego takes care of perception,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the Internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,all the blogamania that goes on there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Essence has to do with the reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the inner reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,how to differentiate appearance from the reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the whole point of spiritual work,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is to be able to distinguish the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than this particular kinesiologic response,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know of no other way of differentiating truth from falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,because man's opinion is frankly worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to tell that to all the bloggers out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's frankly worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we read things, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that the writer hasn't the slightest understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,of what they're writing about,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but they don't let that interfere with expressing their opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's part of the indulgence,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the indulgence of narcissism, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So today we'll be talking about spiritual practice in everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And the kinesiologic response is also correlated with the pupillary response.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody incorrectly compared it to dowsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not dowsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dowsing is a whole different matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and nor does it have anything to do with the unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with the unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with dowsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a response of the energy field of life itself, consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So today I think in between during some of the breaks we're going to be doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,are we going to be doing some pupillary testing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a slit lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we did some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So the pupil responds to truth and falsehood differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So it contracts with one and dilates with the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember which way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have people here who know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's somebody that knows I don't have to bother knowing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,because if they know, it's taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's many physiologic responses,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course we're going to do one chart this morning that demonstrates it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are many physiologic responses,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course the reason we use the kinesiologic response is because it's quick and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just want to restate,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any personal investment or personal stake in the calibrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If it comes up with something you don't like, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I always get a kick out of the emails we get,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.45,0:08:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,because it never dawns on the critic that they could be in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how come you're wrong and calibrated something and so and so, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you're wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The attitude of the student, of course, is to learn all they can learn
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and then wait till grad school to decide if you're wrong or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we've gone over this chart many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so I won't go over it again, but it is just a point of reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So the kinesiologic response, what you're asking is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the essence of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the essence of it, not what is the appearance of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so these may look gorgeous, but they may not be safe to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we'll go to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And, yes, this is just spiritual practices in general,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,which we have done before, and we'll get to the news slides later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just to give you a calibration of feeling of spiritual endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lord's Prayer, 650.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The OM 740 has to be pronounced correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All the OM Manapadma Hum Gregorian chants and Jesus prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and saying the rosary and doing the 12 steps
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and the golden rule and transcendental meditation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and the prayer of Jabez and walking the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you flexion, kneeling to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Devotional acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see where a person who's literal doesn't get what spirituality is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So the criticisms that we get of the work, as bizarre as they get,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,are really limited to people who are limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Their only reality is the pedestrian, linear, concrete world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're unable to interpret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Intuit context, spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's all kinds of things attacking these things as being unscientific.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How can turning a prayer wheel affect God?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,To logic and the skeptic, of course, it sounds ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And bathing in the Ganges, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So to the literalist, no, this is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I advise them, stay away from spirituality and religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like God, stay away from him, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Next thing is, there's all kinds of apologists for what the world calls evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's all kinds of apologists for things that calibrate extremely low.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean extremely low.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bizarrely low.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Has his apologists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And there seems to be, you might say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the human condition is really the people above 200
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,vis-a-vis the people below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really what it amounts to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.67,0:11:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The current calibration of mankind was up to 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It now has come down to 204.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's come down to 204.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,From 207 to 204,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness in America,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,it has come down from 426 to 421.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's correct, yes, 421.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So what goes up can come down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And it shouldn't be too difficult to figure out the likely reasons why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulty with being, the difficulty of trying to cross a bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,which there isn't really a true crossing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is that above 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the brain physiology is different than below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That gives you sort of a limited expectation then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,To people below 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is anything you're saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,does it make any sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can talk to yourself blue in the face,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and they think you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that discouraging?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of being spiritual is to get real,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and stop pretending that this is a dance around the maypole, this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And the difficulty then is the impasse, physiologically,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that even the brains function differently above and below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of that, we get the various physiologic,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,biologic responses that differentiate truth from falsehood,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of which kinesiology is just the most obvious and easy to demonstrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:14:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you can't ask people questions and lay them down and run a slit lamp,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,or check their brain chemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But, so this is a very quick and ready way of discerning truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so that's enough on the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, this isn't supposed to be up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck does this say here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It says spiritual practices, brain function.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It does say spiritual teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we'll get back to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual teachers, we have demonstrated,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and we tried to provide a list so that people don't have to poke through a spiritual library.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A spiritual library has thousands of books in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And which one do you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the next slide, because we can come back to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:15:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We just wanted to reaffirm that we have over a hundred bona fide spiritual teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how exhaustive we make the list,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody will find some weird guru somewhere and pooky doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Baba Gump Gump.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, I don't know about Baba Gump Gump.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You got over a hundred and five good ones here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, can't you find something in English?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Baba Gump Gump.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was finding a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where they find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Some closet somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's somebody who's here from a UFO from the future to tell us what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If they knew what to do, they wouldn't be here from a UFO from the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd know better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go on to the next there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,These are, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, those who doubt the divinity of divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,this is just a reaffirmation that they all calibrate, you know, 850 and higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm screwed up on these things today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain function.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, is that what it says?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It does say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a whole other slide of great spiritual teachers and scriptures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:17:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, a person who is really spiritually committed says, look, this has all been researched already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick one that appeals to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no dearth of bonafide spiritual teachings that calibrate high.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So these books that get a lot of hype in the media, you know, latest discovery, the last something or other, something or other, you know, are all fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all fiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And they appeal to the adventurous child in us who doesn't want to face the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's all very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been written out for hundreds and thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And the point is, you have to apply it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's so much fun to read books and argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We can have theological arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you get through reading all this, if you still have any arguments, call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Move on to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual practices.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,These we've done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is sort of a repetition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a reaffirmation of the calibrated levels of all the spiritual practices because we're going to be talking about them today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the next slide after this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So we were going to, we were just going quickly over the fundamentals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you pick a good teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And to me, a good teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And to me, a good teacher fulfills the obligations of the spiritual teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's two way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A teacher, he doesn't teach all by himself in the middle of the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A teacher, by definition, is one who mixes with students and shares what he's learned and experienced and knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So we put in the obligations of the spiritual teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is to be integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To stick to the truth as he understands it and has experienced it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As it's been revealed to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:19:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, you can tell a spiritual teacher by the, he takes responsibility, stewardship of the knowledge, moral and ethical conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pedophilia is not really the indication of a good teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't exploit others with money, sex, telling them what to do, what to wear, whether to get married, whether to have sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He explains the teachings, makes them available via multiple ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have a certain dedication.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A dedication to the student and to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I never know whether we're having a lecture or a party here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither do you want students to become dependent on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We like to see autonomous study groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Acknowledge the source of the knowledge and it has nothing to do with personal credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The person is not involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And to share the means of access to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we're going to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go on to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I never, these don't seem to be the ones I picked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, provide means of verification of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's books and videos and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain the pitfalls along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Should be transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid seduction by mystification.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejects commercialization.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maintain simplicity of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid glamorization and pomposity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And to me, a truth teacher should be completely transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing, no facade necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the teacher is the reality that has come to take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And replace the personal ego that was there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I am having difficulty because I can't read these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtual practices, well, due to protoplasmic difficulties.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I now have this, hmm, did we do slide 86?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I see, now it's making sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.36,0:21:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Sherlock Holmes, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:22:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, this is what we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we finally got to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.73,0:22:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you make spiritual practice priority?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you make it real?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you make it real?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.49,0:22:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We said that in, traditionally, religion tends to get compartmentalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.49,0:22:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, to Saturday or Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the rest of the week you get back to reality, which is business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't have to feel guilty about things that you would if it was Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so the first thing you want is education.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.90,0:22:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why we provide a list of affirmed hundreds of teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and hundreds of teachings and writings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the beginning you seek education.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.90,0:22:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You explore things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.90,0:22:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also warn people about the pitfalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.90,0:22:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall off into the glamour and the mystification
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and the magic of New Age phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And avoid all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid it because, number one, it's a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Number two, it calibrates below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And thirdly, you can get hooked in it without thinking that you got hooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.90,0:23:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, oh, I walked in and out of there and I didn't believe any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.90,0:23:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Except now you've got a frequency and a vibration in one of your chakras
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that you didn't have before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they collect all kinds of debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.90,0:23:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So then you have to decide through education to choose the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the pathway?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is the pathway that's comfortable for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.99,0:23:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think in a group like this, it's pretty eclectic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.15,0:23:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And people come from diverse backgrounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And they practice diverse many, many different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:24:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of us have been, I was a member of the first Zen Institute in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.22,0:24:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And Zen monasteries, we do various kinds of meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.89,0:24:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We also come from Christian and Jewish and Hebrew backgrounds
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.89,0:24:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and Buddhist backgrounds and every other kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.89,0:24:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sufis, all different kinds of backgrounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, you get attracted to one, usually one predominant pathway.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.46,0:24:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the work that we've done, what we've tried to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.46,0:24:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is distill the essence of truth in all of the pathways.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.46,0:24:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And that saves you a couple of lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.46,0:24:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there is a core of confirmable spiritual truth within all pathways.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.30,0:24:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of fooling around with the externals,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.30,0:24:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you go direct to what is the spiritual core that's intrinsic to all,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.30,0:24:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to any verifiable pathway.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.30,0:24:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the intrinsic core?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.36,0:24:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That eventually leads you to the search for,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.42,0:24:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to the search for enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.42,0:25:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And that eventually leads you to the pathway of non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.84,0:25:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To let go your attachment to the linear
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.84,0:25:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and to realize the source of your existence
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.84,0:25:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,as the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.02,0:25:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So the alignment with the pathway,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.02,0:25:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the pathway we talk about then,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.02,0:25:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is the direct pathway to enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.02,0:25:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And according to our understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.02,0:25:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,according to our understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.14,0:25:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,according to our understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.14,0:25:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the following the direct pathway,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.75,0:25:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the following the direct pathway,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.75,0:25:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,speeds up the likelihood of enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.75,0:25:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,speeds up the likelihood of enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.75,0:25:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,more than 1,000 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.75,0:25:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The likelihood of enlightenment was so rare
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.30,0:25:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The likelihood of enlightenment was so rare
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.30,0:25:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that when it did happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.30,0:25:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,centuries went by which no one became enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.65,0:25:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,now the chances are more than 1,000 times greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.71,0:25:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,More than 1,000 times greater,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.71,0:25:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,because we define what is the essence of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.71,0:25:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that prevails in all spaces.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.81,0:26:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,in all pathways, no matter what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.29,0:26:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth of the realization of the Sufi
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.61,0:26:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,should be the same as the truth of the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.53,0:26:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Buddhist.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.74,0:26:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.58,0:26:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute, I wanna, so everyone can hear you,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.70,0:26:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're not coming across on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.94,0:26:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They heard me say, oh glory be to me, oh Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.71,0:26:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The culture of narcissism.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.77,0:26:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, why is the level in America coming down?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.42,0:26:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of narcissism,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.00,0:26:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's prevailing more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.24,0:26:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the Pope noticed that, and I agree with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.20,0:26:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, glory be to me, oh Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.86,0:26:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.53,0:26:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you find a pathway that appeals to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.67,0:26:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the core and essence of all spiritual pathways?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.55,0:26:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And you find one that you feel comfortable with.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.59,0:27:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And, oh, they say, well, I guess, hmm, I had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.78,0:27:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to our pathways?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.16,0:27:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's, this is the purest of all the pathways.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.35,0:27:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.52,0:27:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you find what you're comfortable with.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.03,0:27:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And you find a teacher that you're comfortable with,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.29,0:27:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,whose teachings are available,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.15,0:27:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and who can be corroborated.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.27,0:27:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't study any teacher that I didn't authenticate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.40,0:27:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.60,0:27:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So you find one.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.54,0:27:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't even read any book.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.60,0:27:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of the people send me all kinds of books,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.24,0:27:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and I say, this one's $2.50.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.28,0:27:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, put it on the pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.50,0:27:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The $2.50 pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.52,0:27:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And because you don't have time to read everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.50,0:27:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and if it's at $2.50, it's not, I mean, it's good,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.34,0:28:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not going to get you to enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.17,0:28:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So you align with the pathway,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.74,0:28:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you commit to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.76,0:28:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you begin to institute a daily routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.28,0:28:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you the routine I followed for a long time was
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.12,0:28:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,an hour of meditation in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.70,0:28:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,an hour of meditation every afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.56,0:28:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,when I was fully engaged in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.54,0:28:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,with a giant psychiatric practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.01,0:28:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, in the evening, going to one spiritual group or another,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.09,0:28:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd rotate spiritual groups, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.77,0:28:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,12-step groups or a meditation group or, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.94,0:28:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there was always some spiritual group,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.46,0:28:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and you finally get a sort of a group of people
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.34,0:28:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that go from one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.18,0:28:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A spiritual group to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.91,0:28:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called keeping holy company, which we'll get to.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.89,0:28:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's finally a commitment that ends up as a daily routine
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.63,0:28:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in which meditation, and we've spoken about meditation before,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.89,0:29:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll make it, I'll just say simply meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.73,0:29:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sit and do it anywhere, anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.66,0:29:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The simplest way is to close your eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.28,0:29:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you look straight ahead with your eyes closed,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.44,0:29:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see very tiny, tiny little lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.42,0:29:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Very tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.78,0:29:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tiny little phosgenes or something they call them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.92,0:29:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And you look beyond that,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.08,0:29:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and eventually, you just don't try to do anything at all
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.58,0:29:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,except to be with the visual field in which nothing is happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.26,0:29:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,which is quite boring, and therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.60,0:29:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you eventually let go of thinking this,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.20,0:29:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and meditation is the whole subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.58,0:29:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've spoken about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.24,0:29:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that the mind eventually comes to a stop
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.96,0:29:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,when you realize that below you,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.48,0:29:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,when you realize that below the mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.64,0:29:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,there's an infinite space of silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.69,0:29:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The thinkingness then interrupts the silence,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.99,0:29:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and how to get beyond the thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.03,0:29:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to the realization of the infinite silence that's below it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.07,0:30:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is done through meditation and contemplation,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.49,0:30:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and prayer and supplication.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.46,0:30:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In contemplation, we've also spoken as a lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.12,0:30:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To contemplate a thing is to sort of hang in with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.62,0:30:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to hang in with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.86,0:30:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and to be with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.08,0:30:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,not to try to do anything with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.92,0:30:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,not to try to understand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.10,0:30:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,not to process it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.59,0:30:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say we take glory to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.37,0:30:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.05,0:30:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All glory be to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.47,0:30:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All glory be to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.64,0:30:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you don't have to,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.02,0:30:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing to think about that, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.96,0:30:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't present anything to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.18,0:30:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more a positioning,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.18,0:30:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of yourself vis-a-vis life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.55,0:30:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory be to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.43,0:30:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All glory be to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.90,0:30:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody wrote me and wants me to say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.66,0:31:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to you, O God.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.04,0:31:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want to say to you, O God.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.12,0:31:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to say to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.99,0:31:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.41,0:31:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if there's a you,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.41,0:31:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,calling God a you,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.12,0:31:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's a me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.11,0:31:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You set up duality instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.76,0:31:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If I talk to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.86,0:31:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,there's got to be a me,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.86,0:31:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,separate from the you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.05,0:31:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It sets up separation as a premise.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.05,0:31:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, God is generic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.91,0:31:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been all kinds of gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.91,0:31:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Germanic gods, mythic gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.91,0:31:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,all kinds of gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.23,0:31:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,God is very generic.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.16,0:31:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When you pray,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.69,0:31:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you want to pray to divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.69,0:31:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Divinity is thee,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.69,0:31:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.39,0:31:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say to God?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.39,0:31:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.58,0:32:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.52,0:32:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So thee infers the divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.84,0:32:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that is being addressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.25,0:32:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory be to thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.25,0:32:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why Lord instead of God?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.98,0:32:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because God doesn't have anything to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.94,0:32:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,God exists independently.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.94,0:32:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Many gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.26,0:32:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Greek gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.38,0:32:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Germanic gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.38,0:32:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,all kinds of gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.38,0:32:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But Lord relates to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.80,0:32:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,means your Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.86,0:32:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your God,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.86,0:32:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's your Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.90,0:32:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever chooses your Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.90,0:32:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is your Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.90,0:32:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.73,0:32:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thee, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.73,0:33:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,expresses tenderness,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.79,0:33:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,mutual ownership,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.14,0:33:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,mutual mutuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.14,0:33:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All glory be to thee,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.39,0:33:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.52,0:33:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lord of all, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.16,0:33:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,relates to you directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.16,0:33:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In all the scriptures,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.38,0:33:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,from no matter what the origin,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.38,0:33:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it says,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.38,0:33:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,those who turn to me
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.18,0:33:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.46,0:33:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So now,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.72,0:33:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.72,0:33:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are owned by the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.72,0:33:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When you call the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.72,0:33:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.72,0:33:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,now you're defining
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.49,0:33:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the relationship to divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.49,0:33:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,which is not a me and a God,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.49,0:33:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,which is not any relationship at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.49,0:33:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Like me and the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.98,0:33:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Unto thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.98,0:33:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Unto thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.58,0:33:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Addressed as Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.58,0:34:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the Lord cannot refuse your entreaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.58,0:34:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.13,0:34:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What I just said is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.67,0:34:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Addressed as thee, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.67,0:34:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity cannot refuse the entreaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.70,0:34:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a fact, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.66,0:34:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.66,0:34:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a fact, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.40,0:34:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You, O God,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.39,0:34:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is a separate thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.39,0:34:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's not obligated.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.78,0:34:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He gets off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.06,0:34:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.13,0:34:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,God,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.13,0:34:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,God prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.13,0:34:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He sits up there
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.13,0:34:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,twiddling some cherubs on his toe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.32,0:34:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, another,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.96,0:34:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, you, God prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.96,0:34:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.66,0:34:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.66,0:34:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he's got to put the cherubs down
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.82,0:34:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and open himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.62,0:35:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because divinity responds to supplication.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.22,0:35:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.31,0:35:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,contemplation is a,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.31,0:35:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,a contemplative lifestyle,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.31,0:35:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,as I've said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.31,0:35:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is a very yin way,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.31,0:35:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like your life becomes a mudra,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.31,0:35:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,by which your supplication,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.31,0:35:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.31,0:35:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically responds.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.98,0:35:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.75,0:35:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To thee, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.18,0:35:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.18,0:35:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,if God is listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.18,0:35:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To thee, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.72,0:35:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,God hears.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.55,0:35:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.55,0:35:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To you, O God,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.58,0:35:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,God is not obligated.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.15,0:35:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.15,0:35:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not obligated.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.15,0:35:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.15,0:35:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not involved, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.15,0:35:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.46,0:35:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.60,0:35:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.60,0:35:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,thee, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.60,0:36:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,indicates devotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.60,0:36:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,devotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.60,0:36:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in all the great,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.60,0:36:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the greats,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.60,0:36:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Krishna,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.60,0:36:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.60,0:36:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who are devoted to me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.60,0:36:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.79,0:36:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough to contemplate on
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.79,0:36:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,for the next couple of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.79,0:36:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could just contemplate that,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.17,0:36:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.17,0:36:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and just hold that,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.42,0:36:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.42,0:36:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,when you reach a state of extreme joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.06,0:36:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.06,0:36:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,when divinity reveals its essence,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.68,0:36:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,one goes into a state of wonderment,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.32,0:36:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which is paralyzing,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.32,0:36:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,wonderment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.14,0:36:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And after you reach that state,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.14,0:36:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to stop it,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.14,0:36:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,or you can't function in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.94,0:36:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.94,0:36:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,as the divinity of all that exists
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.94,0:36:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,reveals itself to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.10,0:36:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you're stunned and into awe,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.10,0:37:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and silent awe,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.10,0:37:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mind never says anything again,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.29,0:37:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.29,0:37:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no person to think,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.29,0:37:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,having witnessed the reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.29,0:37:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.29,0:37:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's silenced forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.29,0:37:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.32,0:37:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,contemplation,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.32,0:37:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,plus prayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.32,0:37:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and you notice I said supplication.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.32,0:37:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Supplication.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.49,0:37:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,To thee, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.49,0:37:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,do I devote my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.52,0:37:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing beyond that,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.98,0:37:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that you,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.98,0:37:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,as a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.98,0:37:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.98,0:37:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.98,0:37:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the ultimate you can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.11,0:37:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.11,0:37:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the ultimate that can be said.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.44,0:37:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.78,0:37:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I like precision.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.29,0:37:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,With humility,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.12,0:38:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,goes humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.12,0:38:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Goes humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.12,0:38:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Goes humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.70,0:38:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody thinks of humor
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.70,0:38:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,as a spiritual practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.70,0:38:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.70,0:38:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it's one of the most powerful ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.89,0:38:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're letting the narcissistic ego
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.89,0:38:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,haste more than being laughed at.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.05,0:38:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.05,0:38:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Nero that declared himself God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.05,0:38:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.05,0:38:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,he declared himself God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.05,0:38:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.05,0:38:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,he must have said,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.05,0:38:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.05,0:38:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,O God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.05,0:38:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We will destroy all of Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.05,0:38:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.05,0:38:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,O God.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.05,0:38:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think humor
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.05,0:38:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of the greatest benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.05,0:38:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.05,0:38:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because humor
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.05,0:38:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is always contrasting
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.05,0:38:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,essence
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.14,0:38:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,with
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.14,0:38:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.14,0:38:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Humor is
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.14,0:38:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,always
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.14,0:38:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,contrasting
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.14,0:38:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,essence
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.14,0:38:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,with
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.14,0:38:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.14,0:38:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Humor is
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.14,0:38:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,always
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.14,0:38:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,contrasting
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.14,0:38:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,essence
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.14,0:38:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,with
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.37,0:38:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.37,0:38:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always contrasting
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.37,0:38:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,how the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.37,0:38:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,or you view something,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.37,0:38:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.37,0:38:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,what the reality is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.37,0:38:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.37,0:38:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.37,0:38:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,it's the contrast
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.37,0:38:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that makes it funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.37,0:38:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the contrast
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.46,0:39:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that makes it funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.46,0:39:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,People that are very,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.72,0:39:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,very serious
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.72,0:39:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,about life
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.72,0:39:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.72,0:39:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.85,0:39:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.85,0:39:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,did you never notice
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.85,0:39:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitler laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.85,0:39:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stalin
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.67,0:39:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.22,0:39:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman Mayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.22,0:39:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Peasants.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.23,0:39:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Peasants.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.23,0:39:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will lead you to freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.82,0:39:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.82,0:39:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,died on his great march?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.62,0:39:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The great leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.62,0:39:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.58,0:39:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,30,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.58,0:39:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,30,000
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.58,0:39:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,died on the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.58,0:39:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.58,0:39:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayo's great
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.47,0:39:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,trick
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.47,0:39:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,across,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.47,0:39:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.92,0:39:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think 30,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.92,0:39:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.98,0:39:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I would call a guy
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.98,0:39:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,who lost 30,000
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.98,0:39:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of his troops
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.98,0:39:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,just going from here
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.98,0:39:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to there
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.98,0:39:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a great leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.98,0:39:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd call him in
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.85,0:39:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,for a hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.52,0:39:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost 30,000
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.52,0:40:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.52,0:40:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,From here
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.52,0:40:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to Phoenix?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.09,0:40:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.09,0:40:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I would call him
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.09,0:40:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the great.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.05,0:40:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.05,0:40:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so humility
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.05,0:40:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.78,0:40:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Humor
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.78,0:40:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and humility
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.78,0:40:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.78,0:40:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.78,0:40:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When you take yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.78,0:40:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,too seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.78,0:40:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you can be carried away
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.85,0:40:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.85,0:40:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you see
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.85,0:40:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,how imbecilic you are
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.85,0:40:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes you laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.85,0:40:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.03,0:40:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dedication
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.03,0:40:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.03,0:40:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dedication.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.47,0:40:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Along the pathway
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.47,0:40:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you become
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.47,0:40:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,increasingly aware
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.47,0:40:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.47,0:40:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.47,0:40:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.47,0:40:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the human perception
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.47,0:40:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,projected onto life
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.47,0:40:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.47,0:40:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the humor
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.47,0:40:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of the contrast
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.47,0:40:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,between reality
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.47,0:40:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.47,0:40:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.46,0:40:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you become
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.46,0:40:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,very dedicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.46,0:40:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The pathway
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.46,0:40:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,or the teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.46,0:40:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that I ascribe
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.46,0:40:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is the pathway
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.46,0:40:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to God
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.46,0:40:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,through absolute
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.46,0:40:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,confirmable
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.46,0:41:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and verifiable
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.46,0:41:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.46,0:41:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.46,0:41:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth itself
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.46,0:41:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is the pathway
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.46,0:41:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.51,0:41:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There are various ways
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.51,0:41:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.51,0:41:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.51,0:41:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're devoted
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.31,0:41:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.31,0:41:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and to honesty
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.31,0:41:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.31,0:41:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and the perfection
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.31,0:41:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.31,0:41:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you become
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.31,0:41:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,increasingly
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.31,0:41:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,sensitive
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.31,0:41:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.31,0:41:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and the beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.31,0:41:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of every
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.98,0:41:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of all
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.98,0:41:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.98,0:41:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You become
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.98,0:41:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,increasingly
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.72,0:41:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.72,0:41:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I always
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.13,0:41:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,advise people
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.13,0:41:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,become aware
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.13,0:41:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of the beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.13,0:41:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,of each thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.13,0:41:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.13,0:41:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,project anything
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.13,0:41:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,onto it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.13,0:41:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.13,0:41:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,its absolute
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.13,0:41:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.58,0:41:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.58,0:41:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,takes a while
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.58,0:41:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,for some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.73,0:41:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.82,0:41:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.82,0:41:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,what it means
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.82,0:41:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.82,0:41:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.27,0:41:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,everything
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.27,0:41:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.27,0:41:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.91,0:41:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If a shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.91,0:41:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,is tattered
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.91,0:42:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.90,0:42:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.08,0:42:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You read
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.88,0:42:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,through your
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.88,0:42:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,favorite shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.90,0:42:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.61,0:42:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,going to the doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.61,0:42:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.15,0:42:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.44,0:42:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,going to the doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.44,0:42:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.44,0:42:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.04,0:42:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.04,0:42:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,she sees
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.34,0:42:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.34,0:42:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.34,0:42:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and I see
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.34,0:42:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.34,0:42:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in torn old shirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.65,0:42:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's actually
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.65,0:42:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,not beauty
